snippet.title: Blood of the Dead Trailer | Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 Zombies
snippet.description:
The undead await in Alcatraz.

This is 'Blood of the Dead' in Call of Duty: Black Ops 4, a reimagined return of a fan-favorite, complete with surprises hidden within the iconic penitentiary.

Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 is available October 12, 2018. Pre-order at participating retailers on disc or digital download: http://bit.ly/PreOrderBO4

New music by Jack Wall @jackwallmusic https://www.facebook.com/jackwallmusic/ http://www.jackwall.net.
New lyrics by Cindy Shapiro @cindyshapiro https://www.cindyshapiro.net/.
Based on original song by Kevin Sherwood & James McCawley.   
Lyrics: Kevin Sherwood.
Choir: Children’s Choir in Los Angeles.
Vocals: Malukah @malukah https://www.youtube.com/malufenix.

Follow us for all the latest intel:

Facebook: http://facebook.com/CallofDuty and http://www.facebook.com/Treyarch/;
Twitter: http://twitter.com/CallofDuty and http://twitter.com/Treyarch;
Instagram: http://instagram.com/CallofDuty and http://www.instagram.com/treyarch/;
